; INPUTS:
;	Data_file 		:The photon list to be processed (Level 2 file).
;	UV_Base_Dir		:The top level UV directory (typically FUV or NUV)
; OUTPUTS:
; OPTIONAL INPUT KEYWORDS:
; NOTES:
;					Data files are written out as per the original names
